text: chitra tu achhi bachiii h mujhe tere character bahot pasand h ak daam mast lagti h pehle tujhe dekke laga me terese ni milpavunggi but baadme realise hua tu sabse se achhese gulmiljati h. mujhe short temper h phirbi tune complaint ni kiya . mene jitna  bi  time spend terese kiya vo achhete memories h . thank you four years mere care lene keliye and help karne keliye. bandariyoki maharani lagti h jab kiran,deepshika,manisha aur anjali ke saath rehti h toh.

text: tu gandi bachhi h galiya bi sikhati h and sare eco ke courses help karvati h. tune mujhe help kiya eco me tu aur vipin ne mere sare eco ke courses karvaye . tere vajase me techkriti show manegment gaye and vaha mene bahot enjoy kiya and Gaurav bi dost hua. tere saath courses break me tea pina , snacks khana and tere saath group banana. me bahot tension letehu but tu mujhe shant karti h. bahot se yade h rajastani bhilli tere saath. tu aur chitra  baat kaam aur galiya zyada bolte h. life long kush raho.
author: Sireesha  Gugulothu

text: vipinaaaaa...... pehli baar chem lab me milata uske baadse 4 years ni choda tujhe mene sareke eco ke courses tere vajase complete huye. tere vajase mene bahot sikha jabbi me kisise gussa hoti hu tu mujhe smjhata  h mere saath bahar jata h jabbi me bhulatihu mujhe bahot baar doubt ata h tujhe gussa kyu ni ata h merepe. but ak cheese achhi lagti h jab tere face dekhna hota h jab me boltihu tu chota aur mouse ki tara h karke boltihu. bahotsi memories h tere saath jo life long yaad rahegi. kabibi tu irritate ni hua jabbi me phone pe bakhvas kartihu . tu mujhe zyada samjhte h and me haar bakvas sunte h. mujhe ni lagta aese dost mujhe milengge iitk baad. tere saath zyada  photos ni h yahi problem h. mujhe pata h mene tujhe bahot pareshan kiya h 4 years but baadme me bi karunggi kisne banaya h tujhe mera friend.
